[SPEAKER_10]: Then the board closed the public portion of the hearing.

346
00:30:37,224 --> 00:30:55,633
[SPEAKER_10]: And at the very start, before we were really deliberating, there was a request from the applicant to continue so that there would be the opportunity to incorporate some of the public comment and revise the plans, which we now saw tonight.

