350
00:31:23,496 --> 00:31:26,718
[SPEAKER_10]: So we're going to limit the public comment

351
00:31:27,454 --> 00:31:36,237
[SPEAKER_10]: especially for anyone who already made a public comment at the last hearing to comments on what has changed in the plan.

352
00:31:37,017 --> 00:31:45,660
[SPEAKER_10]: So if you already participated and you love the plans or you express some concerns with the plans, those are already in the public record.

