356
00:32:03,947 --> 00:32:14,209
[SPEAKER_10]: Also, I know we have a lot of folks on, and so I'm planning to enforce 60 seconds after you introduce yourself per public comment.

357
00:32:15,670 --> 00:32:20,151
[SPEAKER_10]: If we need to, at discretion, we might extend that, but in general, 60 seconds a person.

358
00:32:20,171 --> 00:32:23,432
[SPEAKER_10]: If you already made a comment and your thoughts haven't changed,

359
00:32:24,040 --> 00:32:24,921
[SPEAKER_10]: No need to make it again.

360
00:32:25,421 --> 00:32:35,489
[SPEAKER_10]: But if you have comments on anything that has changed in the plans and how that relates to the board's decision, please feel free to chime in.

361
00:32:36,490 --> 00:32:45,797
[SPEAKER_10]: As we mentioned at the last hearing, the standard here is that of a special permit because a reconstruction

362
00:32:46,734 --> 00:32:50,756
[SPEAKER_10]: can be done by right within the building footprint.

363
00:32:50,816 --> 00:32:52,556
[SPEAKER_10]: This changes the building footprint.

364
00:32:53,236 --> 00:33:07,602
[SPEAKER_10]: And so the standard the board will apply is whether the proposed changes here, whether or not they're substantially more detrimental to the neighborhood than the existing structure.

365
00:33:07,822 --> 00:33:10,203
[SPEAKER_10]: So just wanted to get that all out of the way.

366
00:33:10,223 --> 00:33:15,725
