[SPEAKER_10]: unmute themselves.

368
00:33:18,983 --> 00:33:22,324
[SPEAKER_10]: And so what we're going to do, we're going to use the raised hand cue.

369
00:33:23,064 --> 00:33:26,105
[SPEAKER_10]: When I call on someone, I'll make sure to unmute them.

370
00:33:26,825 --> 00:33:28,366
[SPEAKER_10]: And then you'll have your chance to speak.

371
00:33:28,566 --> 00:33:33,948
