747
01:12:48,366 --> 01:12:56,174
[SPEAKER_26]: The site which the proponent has control over is larger than the housing portion of it, obviously.

748
01:12:56,855 --> 01:13:06,506
[SPEAKER_26]: It was explained that the self-storage part of the site is still a profitable enterprise, and that's why they're keeping that.

749
01:13:07,867 --> 01:13:14,770
[SPEAKER_26]: You know, it's really hard to evaluate this project in the absence of that entire site.

750
01:13:15,130 --> 01:13:29,876
