754
01:13:47,010 --> 01:13:51,274
[SPEAKER_26]: Why are you not considering the site as a whole?

755
01:13:51,794 --> 01:14:04,865
[SPEAKER_26]: And also, I think the neighbors raised very legitimate questions, which is, once you do this part of the site, what's to prevent the self-storage part of the site from being developed in an equally dense manner?

