768
01:15:19,028 --> 01:15:21,770
[SPEAKER_25]: whereas this space has been underutilized.

769
01:15:22,130 --> 01:15:30,193
[SPEAKER_25]: And so the opportunity on a large site like this is to develop housing that meets the needs of the community and the region.

770
01:15:31,734 --> 01:15:42,899
[SPEAKER_25]: And so the 40B comprehensive permit application focuses on a three and a half acre portion of the overall large site.

771
01:15:44,040 --> 01:15:48,162
[SPEAKER_25]: That is the project that is squarely in this board's

772
01:15:49,223 --> 01:15:49,643
[SPEAKER_25]: domain.

