01:15:50,523 --> 01:15:52,184
[SPEAKER_25]: And it's an industrial district.

774
01:15:52,244 --> 01:16:02,348
[SPEAKER_25]: We've identified the reasons why we think this is a transitional use is appropriate between industry and between a residential neighborhood.

775
01:16:04,288 --> 01:16:12,631
[SPEAKER_25]: And certainly the remaining industrial property could be redeveloped in the future.

776
01:16:13,471 --> 01:16:18,133
